{"title":"What is the problem in Australia? (from my email)","link":"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/892438031/0/marginalrevolution~What-is-the-problem-in-Australia-from-my-email.html","date":1714676864000,"content":"<p>From Khalil Menaf Hegarty, note that an Australian dollar is worth about 65 cents.  I also won’t double indent:</p>\r\n<p>“There are a series of economy-wide, labour-related problems in Australia that policymakers appear incapable of tackling in a coherent way.</p>\r\n<p>First up, <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://secure-web.cisco.com/1AVvXyjlbONVGhNaBfqs2Zev7nv2twQ7iL-yoIAdK43514kq5hVSHfOVpOG0Ifu-TskRu1TUxI6Q0yOTKkWrncfG7FQGkZxKbcro5DlNIwhG40G7Qtcr_1OI_UoX0_Ifhrh6i7m8piCjGWd_V-EgJDSbaGs_4faLVFutCudvTBqMt8D-ONWNdAxbYDRc5IaoEGiA_piNsKR2TbhjWwlmaUrBPH9MQTKAg76HS7acCaaISGxrQ7qIiNGgp-sK7K5H3Kli06jRTQRGxODGwEg1X0FPKoU9HYKYo9WuRleuczGsfPyMpvpxgic5PAEtls4AFLTwKwOXrLevz5scWFmE-eEdYIzqrkFFR0tclQyAmCMzXpnU98l7KgSrJFH-BBZ2ZhTrKsSJUSTBYiqr6cSru31mTiemStNyMtKwApH5vYv-1dtiXM9DdDaS6gOSohI-o/https%3A%2F%2Fwww.macrobusiness.com.au%2F2024%2F04%2Faustralias-never-ending-per-capita-recession%2F\" target=\"_blank\">this is a very good summary</a> of some key national indicators around Australia’s per capita recession.</p>\r\n<p>The story <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://secure-web.cisco.com/1rEHWrS0Ah1fhZVLfihykuU-qABtU4JElnQp5Mym7GjckWC9Cg252iGBWBKB8GNH8iPrSzsSI_dwH-7TUZzi_1-8L89FDCvgGNIskRmRMjLMddNY-LiZwyqrZ1bKFUFBCkwXp5YZPaHAMgjMNPVqhw0XytpgM1Uud0AkchjAa0GfOjtj4MNTnxw1DSaes_3mkw9DIzCB23vmY4_3Pd3eU43skjEbOXYLnNCxI4kbGkD0ycvXorccDMBI6E1TaA9hiW8F4oblMw_I_RWx3OT88sAfV8gSfIHrLTEdNqaWCnK0uvlPtn3vsJ0kHfuExLuxBC2e1vYqpIP0C6cK1dNYOXHJcIpY0Iz7119K4Zz9QTOSTPPPHil10VZiipFhInSZUYAYvVUwJCvm2wXw-iC2X8nh3Mh5OaI8ciA3Cd3_wzPlvlSlpU0yt1d6UUg3AcU8p/https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.com.au%2Ffinance%2Fwork%2Fat-work%2Fcity-held-hostage-as-tradies-demand-240k-salary%2Fnews-story%2Fab39e7a1a7f9ee892d2c6a4e3b295c30\" target=\"_blank\">here</a> is a good entry point to what is happening on the ground, but I’ll try and summarise.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Left-leaning state governments have embarked on major infrastructure projects (and require significant public debt);</li>\r\n<li>These projects require minimum pay requirements that are effectively endorsed by construction unions;</li>\r\n<li>Costs and wages tend to blow out for these reasons (and I don’t want to get into the public debt conversation here);</li>\r\n<li>As noted in the story, the wage demands are quite significant. (AUD240k = approx. USD160k)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>At the same time:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Significant labour shortages in <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://secure-web.cisco.com/172s2bgx7f-lrKRUX3__Bk_TdUg8qxPWPTkTaP5Uo_qqDo-QqRbkmu_O_5IZ6IQbsfU6BR6aNZMx9qRLuPc5YxPpPqgCRK0LpvlBg8OYMQk4RybaNsbAaaZJHMnmWgPfE59bqJH9d0uvmRDeFweE3FE4VP0HlsWqwl1hdFG7L23BAojgXXAzWlyQn4kwYH8U-pQwc-HZL0MAVeQTCz64xeyOTF8VwMXQU5kjuaambZy0rygg5xQGBPyJa4XPN1Gr1A07VY5xoSIG0mvagz3Rr5qxx07Y1KFnEoxuPNh2-yegvEuRugaOmjqWmRf9WU5N7y17U3da_C5wDBTPgA47Qy09KO4lT30xdwH0Lo8Y508IRJjL2bGCgkgBZ5Bxj0OviaEOndUvdO1siGngwVGA0pxU36EmJ9hP6TUlfNyphD9Nfny-VHMfOkyfudgBlwmv7/https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sbs.com.au%2Fnews%2Fpodcast-episode%2Fteacher-shortages-persisting-across-the-country%2Fh09seli2t\" target=\"_blank\">teaching</a>, healthcare/<a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://secure-web.cisco.com/1V09jSGF3_F6jcr6pt3ggP0ykR20Iw-bgNgJVHPYtIWKV18q2ObiaAfTTtQvVe_i2FVD25y4vtVeQEilUGca7v1DXpv_fMBWWR7bUOs2BV0pjeRgMY6B0IcZ3GEZFcu_BAC0sh2XgGiEsbOfDzq8rRFlahh5TLIAEPX2FY53fl8SR-eILZgL7_gLksFjKbfIs37CUBXgyw3gxDmpdmOJrC0s7G5g4BgFQbBbYAGaNu5AVbiB4r7orCqcy80Qqx1bFNNO535X_NNmwbzzFIZFpj3x-3YV10OhYtIdY-oeKqevU7pUQmCZFZmzeH8mi-it61B5CODqwM5IaQAzCO3m8CT5iszOHfU9YfV52DwoSwGQG4gVZ9ZyfDKVQ6edjDWTraGIfRTclNhPnwI7HuhrPw6WcdBaHRnqzqG61HmB1OxU27NG7n41sm8-2MMkx-SFS/https%3A%2F%2Finsideageing.com.au%2Fau